'''印度計劃與管理學院'''（'''Indian Institute of Planning and Management'''，縮寫：'''IIPM'''）是一家未被[[印度|印度]]教育系統認可的教育機構，校區位於[[新德里|新德里]]。該學院創立於1973年，提供商科相關的本科到博士學習項目。<ref name="Pioneer story">{{cite news |url=http://www.dailypioneer.com/247366/IIPM-An-intriguing-story-of-growth-and-envy.html |title=An Intriguing Story of Growth and Envy |date=7 April 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100411230440/http://www.dailypioneer.com/247366/IIPM-An-intriguing-story-of-growth-and-envy.html |archivedate=2010年4月11日 |accessdate=5 May 2013 |work=The Pioneer |publisher=CMYK Printech Ltd. |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="IIPMPartner">{{cite web |url=http://www.iipm.in/partner-universities |title=Partner Universities |author=Unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401220526/http://www.iipm.in/partner-universities |archivedate=2013年4月1日 |publisher=The Indian Institute of Planning and Management |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015年4月4日 }}</ref> 

該學院因過度宣傳而多次引發爭議，印度的法定大學評定機構[[大學撥款委員會_(印度)|大學撥款委員會]]多次公示IIPM並未獲得國家認可，其所提供的課程也完全無效。<ref name="indiatoday-bribes">{{cite news |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/ugc-aicte-corrupt-iipm-arindam-chaudhuri-web-pages/1/250580.html |title=UGC, AICTE full of bribe-seeking corrupt officials, says IIPM |first=Ritika |last=Chopra |work=India Today |publisher=Living Media India Limited |date=17 February 2013 |accessdate=1 May 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125043/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/ugc-aicte-corrupt-iipm-arindam-chaudhuri-web-pages/1/250580.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> IIPM回應稱它自己根本就不是大學，也不頒發學位。<ref name="bs-regs">{{cite web |date=23 February 2013 |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/management/iipm-dares-to-take-on-the-regulators-113022300309_1.html |title=IIPM dares to take on the regulators |accessdate=5 May 2013 |first=M. |last=Saraswathy |work=Business Standard |publisher=Business Standard Ltd. |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116121415/https://www.business-standard.com/article/management/iipm-dares-to-take-on-the-regulators-113022300309_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2014年9月德里高等法院判定該校故意誤導學生，并禁止該校使用[[MBA|MBA]]、[[BBA|BBA]]等字眼來描述自己的項目。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.livemint.com/Politics/bKbeznpnmhgfLJdlbKELJL/High-court-censures-IIPM-Arindam-Chaudhuri-for-misleading-s.html |title=High court censures IIPM, Arindam Chaudhuri for misleading students |access-date=2015-04-04 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112161627/https://www.livemint.com/Politics/bKbeznpnmhgfLJdlbKELJL/High-court-censures-IIPM-Arindam-Chaudhuri-for-misleading-s.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年7月，IIPM宣布将关闭所有教育项目并关闭所有[[德里|德里]]外的校区，宣称今后将通过第三方机构来提供教育服务。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iipm.edu/public/admission_details.html |title=IIPM notice |accessdate=2015-07-02 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111074709/http://www.iipm.edu/public/admission_details.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/iipm-to-shut-down-all-campuses-october-onwards-115070201044_1.html |title=IIPM to shut down all campuses October onwards |newspaper=Business Standard |date=2015-07-02 |author=M Saraswathy |accessdate=2016-02-25 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113041234/https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/iipm-to-shut-down-all-campuses-october-onwards-115070201044_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==爭議==
早在得到國際關注之前，就有多家印度媒體和博客報道了此學院自我宣傳的事件，但該校均予以否認。2013年2月[[瓜廖爾|瓜廖爾]]的地區法院要求印度電信部封禁IIPM的78個[[Url|網址]]。<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/NewDelhi/78-web-pages-of-IIPM-including-UGC-s-blocked/Article1-1012746.aspx |title=78 web pages of IIPM including UGC's blocked |work=Hindustan Times |date=16 February 2013 |accessdate=1 May 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503165722/http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/NewDelhi/78-web-pages-of-IIPM-including-UGC-s-blocked/Article1-1012746.aspx |archivedate=2013年5月3日 }}</ref> 《The Hindu》稱IIPM曾借用其名義散發虛假廣告，<ref>{{cite news |title=IIPM’s claim on The Hindu: A clarification |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/iipms-claim-on-the-hindu-a-clarification/article4530742.ece |first=Siddharth |last=Varadarajan |accessdate=21 March 2013 |newspaper=The Hindu |publisher=HT Media Ltd.date=21 March 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212644/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/iipms-claim-on-the-hindu-a-clarification/article4530742.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年12月[[德里高等法院|德里高等法院]]禁止該校於取得法庭許可之前，在任何電視、印刷或在線媒體上發佈廣告，并稱其以前的廣告誤導了大眾。<ref name=livemint>{{Cite web |url=http://www.livemint.com/Politics/PCSynJqOEfVxinlasU5sDJ/Delhi-high-court-says-IIPM-cant-publish-ads-without-its-app.html |title=Delhi high court says IIPM can’t publish ads without its approval |access-date=2015-04-04 |archive-date=2018-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211194429/https://www.livemint.com/Politics/PCSynJqOEfVxinlasU5sDJ/Delhi-high-court-says-IIPM-cant-publish-ads-without-its-app.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=firstpost>{{Cite web |url=http://www.firstpost.com/business/delhi-high-court-bars-iipm-from-advertising-without-court-ok-1270777.html |title=Delhi High Court bars IIPM from advertising without Court OK |access-date=2015-04-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024055/https://www.firstpost.com/business/delhi-high-court-bars-iipm-from-advertising-without-court-ok-1270777.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===維基百科===
據報道，IIPM曾在[[英語維基百科|英語維基百科]]上僱傭編輯操控其條目內容，名為Wifione的英文維基百科管理員亦捲入其中，進而引發醜聞。後者被控操控IIPM條目，刪除其中對該校不利的信息。此用戶使用了最少60個[[分身ID|傀儡]]以操控維基百科中關於此條目的輿論導向。2015年2月，Wifione因此事被維基百科上的[[仲裁委員會_(英語維基百科)|仲裁委員會]]封禁。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/stoi/deep-focus/Wiki-paid-y-a/articleshow/28695840.cms|title=Wiki-paid-y a?|last=Soman|first=Sandhya|date=2014-01-12|access-date=2014-01-12|archive-date=2019-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206141407/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/stoi/deep-focus/Wiki-paid-y-a/articleshow/28695840.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="newsweek-wikiban">{{cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/2015/04/03/manipulating-wikipedia-promote-bogus-business-school-316133.html |title=Manipulating Wikipedia to Promote a Bogus Business School |work=Newsweek.com |date=2015-03-24 |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2015-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703213410/http://www.newsweek.com/2015/04/03/manipulating-wikipedia-promote-bogus-business-school-316133.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="The Hindu-Comments">{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-opinion/the-web-app-that-made-information-free/article7062887.ece|title=The web app that made information free|work=thehindu.com|date=2015-04-03|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124203033/https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-opinion/the-web-app-that-made-information-free/article7062887.ece}}</ref>

